TutoCompleteText.SourceString: Congratulations! You have completed the tutorial level.

TutoAlreadyCompleteText.SourceString: This tutorial section has already been completed. The Bloodpoint reward is only granted for the first time the tutorial is completed.

Text.SourceString: Certain actions may occasionally produce a "Skill Check". Escaping a trial alive will require a combination of teamwork and competence. Failing to time Skill Checks consistently may make survival more challenging.
